\r\n   foot-gun for anyone that turns this feature on\r\n2. Sending task logs in a span seems too large, and way too verbose to provide\r\n   any use in a span.','2024-11-13 01:22:12','ashb'),(3543,'edb3fe08f2887f939363c63c9e7fe85e178c0415','19864447','Update the \"legacy command\" help text for backfill (#43764)\n\nIn 1.x there was an `airflow backfill` command.  In 2.x it became `airflow dags backfill`.\r\n\r\nIn 3.x it\'s back to `airflow backfill`.\r\n\r\nNeed to update the \"yo, your command been moved\" text.','2024-11-12 23:20:15','dstandish'),(3544,'f924ecb6e3d6e85a83b261cc7adc3a3c05c2b1ee','19864447','AIP-84 Migrate test a connection to FastAPI API (#43766)\n\n* Migrate test a connection to fastapi\r\n\r\n* Remove NotFound error from docs\r\n\r\n* Remove Validation error which is handled by fastapi\r\n\r\n* Remove async for complying convention for methods\r\n\r\n* Fix pre-commit ruff','2024-11-12 17:00:16','bugraoz93'),(3545,'ed31b02ce154ef12f6c81cac0bfc2cc6f0dcb1f2','19864447','Fix pre-commit selective checks (#43931)','2024-11-12 16:37:40','pierrejeambrun'),(3546,'32175768c1e47afa82f05419367c2ec206376e0b','19864447','AIP-84 Migrating GET ASSETS Legacy API to fastAPI (#43783)\n\n* AIP-84: Migrating GET Assets to fastAPI\r\n\r\n* matching response to legacy\r\n\r\n* Adding unit tests - part 1\r\n\r\n* Update airflow/api_fastapi/common/parameters.py\r\n\r\nCo-authored-by: Jed Cunningham <66968678+jedcunningham@users.noreply.github.com>\r\n\r\n* fixing the dag_ids filter\r\n\r\n* fixing the dag_ids filter\r\n\r\n* Adding unit tests - part 2\r\n\r\n* fixing unit tests & updating parameter type\r\n\r\n* review comments pierre\r\n\r\n* fixing last commit\r\n\r\n* fixing unit tests\r\n\r\n---------\r\n\r\nCo-authored-by: Jed Cunningham <66968678+jedcunningham@users.noreply.github.com>','2024-11-12 16:04:10','amoghrajesh'),(3547,'d23fe09ab1d870ec6024c537b0c53588df6df80a','19864447','[Edge]Add child processes to separate process group than main (#43927)\n\n* Block