anged documentation for\r\nthe provider and such commits were not included.\r\n\r\nThis PR adds documentation folder to be used while checkign for\r\nthe commit list, and next time when documentation will be generated\r\nfor providers, the doc-only commits should also be included for\r\nall historical versions of providers.','2024-10-31 09:15:58','potiuk'),(3757,'db4afd793a632bfbebd77e495a0c5d0f9b59f366','19864447','DOC fix documentation error in `apache-airflow-providers-fab/access-control.rst` (#43495)\n\n* fix doc error for provider fab\r\n\r\n* Update docs/apache-airflow-providers-fab/auth-manager/access-control.rst\r\n\r\n---------\r\n\r\nCo-authored-by: Elad Kalif <45845474+eladkal@users.noreply.github.com>','2024-10-31 08:47:19','SuccessMoses'),(3758,'568c0352f110c18ec1d0100b0a433da597c84b6e','19864447','Fix main: ignore spell check Uncompress (#43538)\n\n* ignore spell check Uncompress\r\n\r\n* change to lowercase','2024-10-31 08:21:47','gopidesupavan'),(3759,'c42b1d3acd5389d94a4a53fb59fa76278cc91adf','19864447','Update providers metadata 2024-10-31 (#43539)','2024-10-31 07:54:24','eladkal'),(3760,'d3e181215218ca9d0fb510c29d646c2aea315fcb','19864447','Remove `TaskInstanceKey.reduced` (#43532)\n\nNot sure why this was deferred in https://github.com/apache/airflow/pull/39336/files#r1594440137 but I can\'t find any usages of this in the codebase.','2024-10-31 01:17:47','kaxil'),(3761,'a923a83338a2f598dc733553cfc04cfa5ba0d1eb','19864447','Bump `uv` to `0.4.29` (#43531)\n\nhttps://github.com/astral-sh/uv/releases/tag/0.4.29','2024-10-31 01:02:10','kaxil'),(3762,'15ae7ce9724871ad07f81a4a322156280d7ca03c','19864447','Remove deprecated functions from `airflow/configuration.py` (#43530)\n\nThese functions have been deprecated from a long time now.','2024-10-31 00:55:10','kaxil'),(3763,'31ee7cbe5d60f429b7d1e778524bfa5dc1720b5b','19864447','Remove `task_fail` from `airflow db cleanup` (#43528)\n\nThis was missed in https://github.com/apache/airflow/pull/43490','2024-10